<p>После нажать "Далее".</p>
<p>6. Просто нажать "Далее":</p>
<figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://partisans-by.github.io/tg/media/posts/6//Image-040.png" sizes="(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px" srcset="https://partisans-by.github.io/tg/media/posts/6//responsive/Image-040-xs.png 300w ,https://partisans-by.github.io/tg/media/posts/6//responsive/Image-040-sm.png 480w ,https://partisans-by.github.io/tg/media/posts/6//responsive/Image-040-md.png 749w"  alt="" width="1692" height="1092"></figure>
<p>7. Просто нажать "Далее":</p>
<figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://partisans-by.github.io/tg/media/posts/6//Image-041.png" sizes="(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px" srcset="https://partisans-by.github.io/tg/media/posts/6//responsive/Image-041-xs.png 300w ,https://partisans-by.github.io/tg/media/posts/6//responsive/Image-041-sm.png 480w ,https://partisans-by.github.io/tg/media/posts/6//responsive/Image-041-md.png 749w"  alt="" width="1692" height="1092"></figure>
