<figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://partisans-by.github.io/tg/media/posts/6/Image-020.png" sizes="(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px" srcset="https://partisans-by.github.io/tg/media/posts/6/responsive/Image-020-xs.png 300w ,https://partisans-by.github.io/tg/media/posts/6/responsive/Image-020-sm.png 480w ,https://partisans-by.github.io/tg/media/posts/6/responsive/Image-020-md.png 749w"  alt="" width="1692" height="1092"></figure>
<p>17. Указать примерно на 20% меньше, чем максимальный размер тома:</p>
